  <section class="course-str m-below container deled-content">
    <h3>Course Structure</h3>
    <p>The 2-years D. El. Ed. programme is divided into four semesters. While on the one hand the 1st and 2nd semesters cover the pedagogical course of the primary level, on the other hand the 3rd and 4th semester cover the pedagogical course of the upper primary level. Besides, the Foundation Course, Practical Works and School Experience Programmes are included in all the semesters</p>
